     * [file://localhost/Users/admin/Pros/sh/awesome/awe_raw/progressive-e
       nhancement-resources#the-concept]The Concept
     * [file://localhost/Users/admin/Pros/sh/awesome/awe_raw/progressive-e
       nhancement-resources#strategies]Strategies
     * [file://localhost/Users/admin/Pros/sh/awesome/awe_raw/progressive-e
       nhancement-resources#feature-detection]Feature Detection
     * [file://localhost/Users/admin/Pros/sh/awesome/awe_raw/progressive-e
       nhancement-resources#support-tables]Support Tables
     * [file://localhost/Users/admin/Pros/sh/awesome/awe_raw/progressive-e
